Hello. Can I order food by myself?

16
00:01:44,690 --> 00:01:46,349
Sorry, you'll have to book a table first.

17
00:01:46,350 --> 00:01:48,570
Do you have a reservation?

18
00:01:48,570 --> 00:01:51,650
Never mind, thank you.

19
00:02:12,570 --> 00:02:14,550
Zaizai? Zaizai?

20
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:17,909
It's done?

21
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:21,389
No. President Wei drinks a lot.

22
00:02:21,390 --> 00:02:24,770
I bet it will go on for quite a while.

23
00:02:26,230 --> 00:02:27,930
You must be starving.

24
00:02:27,930 --> 00:02:30,149
I brought a few buns for you.

25
00:02:30,149 --> 00:02:33,550
But they've gone cold.

26
00:02:34,510 --> 00:02:36,510
Thanks.

27
00:02:36,510 --> 00:02:39,530
It's just bad luck that you run into this kind of thing.

28
00:02:39,530 --> 00:02:42,829
Manager Chen told me you could go home.

29
00:02:42,829 --> 00:02:48,829
If President Wei sees you when he comes out and starts going amok, you'll be in trouble.

30
00:02:48,829 --> 00:02:50,630
Yes.

31
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:53,170
I've been out for some time. I should get back inside.

32
00:02:53,170 --> 00:02:54,290
Stay safe.

33
00:02:54,290 --> 00:02:56,110
Okay. Don't worry.

34
00:03:33,510 --> 00:03:35,390
 Is it over? 

35
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:37,590
 Did everything go well? 

36
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:58,500
Let me guess, a celebration party?

37
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,290
 Rang Rang. 

38
00:04:01,790 --> 00:04:03,890
W-What's wrong?

39
00:04:03,890 --> 00:04:05,169
It's nothing.

40
00:04:05,170 --> 00:04:07,590
Did you have your dinner?

41
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:09,250
Yes.

42
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:11,369
Dinner was great.

43
00:04:11,370 --> 00:04:17,350
We had roasted duck, brined chicken, candied apple,

44
00:04:17,350 --> 00:04:19,930
and spicy boiled meat slices.

45
00:04:19,930 --> 00:04:21,649
 They were delicious. 

46
00:04:21,650 --> 00:04:25,710
If that's the case, why are you crying?

47
00:04:25,710 --> 00:04:28,529
I saw a bus stop just now.

48
00:04:28,530 --> 00:04:30,210
It says "Jiangyi Road."

49
00:04:30,210 --> 00:04:32,429
I got homesick all of a sudden.

50
00:04:32,429 --> 00:04:33,849
 I'll go to you. 

51
00:04:33,850 --> 00:04:35,369
It's late.

52
00:04:35,370 --> 00:04:36,390
Rang Rang.

53
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:39,990
I'll buy a ticket for the earliest trip home tomorrow.

54
00:04:43,450 --> 00:04:44,850
Rang Rang.

55
00:04:45,670 --> 00:04:47,910
I didn't make a mistake, right?

56
00:04:49,890 --> 00:04:52,430
 Yes, you didn't. 

57
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,750
It's all right.

58
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,970
Everything will be all right soon.

59
00:04:59,970 --> 00:05:02,369
My phone will be power-off. I'll talk to you later.

60
00:05:02,370 --> 00:05:04,410
Rest early.

61
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:06,690
 Okay. 

62
00:05:18,645 --> 00:05:19,789
   

63
