64
00:05:32,110 --> 00:05:33,389
Do you want to get on?

65
00:05:33,389 --> 00:05:36,809
This is the last bus. Miss it and you won't get home.

66
00:05:36,809 --> 00:05:38,129
I don't live here.

67
00:05:38,130 --> 00:05:39,209
Oh.

68
00:05:39,210 --> 00:05:41,250
You should go home.

69
00:05:51,569 --> 00:05:52,889
   

70
00:05:52,890 --> 00:05:57,710
 I wish there was an Anywhere Door of Doraemon right here. 

71
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:04,209
 You are in the wrong this time. 

72
00:06:04,210 --> 00:06:08,169
 You've been working for so long, but can't you handle such social gatherings? 

73
00:06:08,169 --> 00:06:10,290
 Reflect on it. 

74
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:31,030
Why are you here?

75
00:06:32,730 --> 00:06:34,690
I know you've been mistreated.

76
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:37,730
So I came to take you home.

77
00:07:41,650 --> 00:07:43,230
Is it good?

78
00:07:43,230 --> 00:07:44,870
Delicious.

79
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:57,310
Rang Rang. You drove for three hours.

80
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:59,670
Aren't you tired?

81
00:08:00,470 --> 00:08:04,170
Well... I am.

82
00:08:04,170 --> 00:08:08,190
Don't you find me a nuisance?

83
00:08:12,370 --> 00:08:15,150
If I didn't go there,

84
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:17,390
I'd never sleep soundly tonight.

85
00:08:19,550 --> 00:08:21,050
Zaizai.

86
00:08:22,610 --> 00:08:27,410
Not everything should be weighed for its worth in the world.

87
00:08:28,250 --> 00:08:30,710
If it's possible,

88
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:34,290
I'd like you to trouble me more often.

89
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:39,510
What's wrong?

90
00:08:40,310 --> 00:08:43,670
My mom always says the others' words fall on deaf ears,

91
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:45,850
that they go through my ears and not my mind.

92
00:08:45,850 --> 00:08:49,690
If I cover my ears, I can keep your words in mind.

93
00:08:54,610 --> 00:08:57,010
- Dig in. 
 - Okay.

94
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:03,950
It's been a while since I last cooked. Is it too salty?

95
00:09:04,850 --> 00:09:07,410
No. It's even a little sweet.

96
00:09:07,410 --> 00:09:11,610
Maybe the cook was overloaded with sweetness.

97
00:09:16,627 --> 00:09:17,686
   

98
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:19,850
 Tonight? 

99
00:09:19,850 --> 00:09:21,190
Yes.

100
00:09:21,190 --> 00:09:23,569
A friend of mine opened a restaurant.

101
00:09:23,570 --> 00:09:26,690
Well... It's a new restaurant in town. He wants me to try it out.

102
00:09:26,690 --> 00:09:29,110
I thought it'd be boring to eat alone.

103
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:31,410
I wonder if you have the time.

104
00:09:32,190 --> 00:09:34,950
 But I have some other plans tonight I can't turn down now. 

105
00:09:34,950 --> 00:09:36,569
Oh, it's all right.

106
00:09:36,570 --> 00:09:39,190
We'll go there another time.

107
00:09:39,190 --> 00:09:42,089
 Sure. Try the food for me. 

108
00:09:42,090 --> 00:09:45,690
Sure. I should hang up now. Bye.

109
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:50,290
Well...

110
00:09:50,291 --> 00:09:51,738
   

111
00:09:59,490 --> 00:10:01,570
Hello? A'Rang?

112
00:10:02,330 --> 00:10:05,110
So this is the important matter you mentioned?

113
00:10:05,110 --> 00:10:08,409
For me, eating is a priority in life.

114
00:10:08,410 --> 00:10:12,330
Besides, this is a couples' restaurant with good online ratings.

115
00:10:13,710 --> 00:10:18,430
It's a couples' restaurant, but we are here for one thing only.

116
00:10:18,430 --> 00:10:20,150
The food.

117
00:10:21,070 --> 00:10:22,470
Sit down.

118
00:10:29,410 --> 00:10:32,350
Guan Fang? Gu Ran?

119
00:10:34,950 --> 00:10:36,730
So this is the restaurant you mentioned?

120
00:10:36,730 --> 00:10:39,470
- Oh, I came here with a friend. 
 - Jiang Jia!

121
00:10:43,190 --> 00:10:45,910
I have things to discuss. I should head over there.

122
00:10:46,629 --> 00:10:50,510
Sure. We'll talk another time.

123
00:10:59,420 --> 00:11:00,810
Was it hard to find this place?

124
00:11:00,810 --> 00:11:02,470
This is rare.

125
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:06,970
Jiang Jia came to a couples' restaurant with a guy.

126
00:11:07,950 --> 00:11:10,010
They don't look like a couple.

127
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:12,550
No idea.

128
00:11:12,550 --> 00:11:14,730
Are you done? I need the menu.

129
00:11:26,550 --> 00:11:29,830
Why haven't you confessed to Jiang Jia?

130
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:32,929
Is it... Is it that obvious?

131
00:11:32,929 --> 00:11:34,309
It is too obvious.

132
00:11:34,309 --> 00:11:37,650
Everyone can tell. Right?

133
00:11:40,230 --> 00:11:43,509
Yes, it's obvious. I knew it all along.

134
00:11:51,230 --> 00:11:55,670
It's not easy to tell someone that you like them.

135
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:02,930
The type Jiang Jia likes

136
00:12:02,930 --> 00:12:04,950
is someone like Qianyu.

137
00:12:04,950 --> 00:12:07,930
He's kind and thoughtful.

138
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:13,310
I'm afraid to ask her if she likes me.

139
00:12:13,310 --> 00:12:16,630
I'm even more scared to tell her I like her.

140
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:21,170
Being her good friend sounds like a nice excuse.

141
00:12:21,860 --> 00:12:24,970
I can turn my heartfelt words into jokes,

142
00:12:24,970 --> 00:12:29,830
give away the gift I bought on a whim as a free sample.

143
00:12:29,830 --> 00:12:32,370
But if the confession fails,

144
00:12:32,370 --> 00:12:35,170
things will get awkward between us.

145
00:12:35,170 --> 00:12:37,330
She might ignore me for good.

146
00:12:37,850 --> 00:12:41,110
I can't even imagine that.

147
00:12:41,110 --> 00:12:45,330
It's good enough to be good friends.

148
00:12:45,330 --> 00:12:49,929
At least fighting and arguments won't take us apart that easily.

149
00:12:54,350 --> 00:12:58,109
So... It's good that you're not confessing.

150
00:12:58,109 --> 00:12:59,590
I'll confess to her.

151
00:12:59,590 --> 00:13:00,870
 What? 

152
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:03,069
That is the right thing to do!

153
00:13:03,069 --> 00:13:07,029
If you never make an impulsive move, you will always regret it.

154
00:13:07,029 --> 00:13:10,431
- Go, do it now. 
 - Hey... Hold on.

155
00:13:10,431 --> 00:13:14,230
But... You need preparation to win a girl's heart.

156
00:13:14,230 --> 00:13:16,150
So I need your advice on this.

157
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:17,230
I need your experience.

158
00:13:17,230 --> 00:13:19,329
I have no such experience.

159
00:13:19,329 --> 00:13:21,210
You get it.

160
00:13:21,210 --> 00:13:24,150
I've been in a dozen of relationships.

161
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:26,870
But it all ended in failure. Do you still want my advice?

162
00:13:26,870 --> 00:13:29,410
I knew I couldn't count on you.

163
00:13:29,410 --> 00:13:32,430
I must rely on myself.

164
00:13:34,030 --> 00:13:36,350
What is your plan?

165
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:44,409
Jiang Jia loves hotpot, crayfish, noodles with soybean paste, and ice cream.

166
00:13:44,409 --> 00:13:47,250
These have to be the topics she likes.

167
00:13:49,010 --> 00:13:50,650
Gu Ran?

168
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:56,170
Did you just happen to come here after a walk again?

169
00:13:56,670 --> 00:14:00,089
Yeah. Did you just have dinner?

170
00:14:00,089 --> 00:14:01,590
Yes.

171
00:14:04,850 --> 00:14:06,470
What did you have?

172
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:08,170
Dumplings.

173
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:11,269
- Dumplings? 
 - Yeah.

174
00:14:14,770 --> 00:14:17,270
Freshly made or frozen?

175
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:19,030
Freshly made.

176
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:20,610
Freshly made.

177
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:22,949
Good. That is good.

178
00:14:22,949 --> 00:14:24,490
Good.

179
00:14:25,610 --> 00:14:30,210
So, don't stay up too late. I should get going.

180
00:14:33,210 --> 00:14:35,010
Gu Ran.

181
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:38,690
Are you...

182
00:14:43,710 --> 00:14:46,590
It's nothing. I'm heading inside.

183
00:14:46,590 --> 00:14:48,190
Good night.

184
00:14:59,810 --> 00:15:02,670
I think my effort yields some positive results.

185
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:04,670
She said good night to me.

186
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:06,249
She said good night!

187
00:15:06,250 --> 00:15:08,970
Don't you think the hint is obvious enough?

188
00:15:09,690 --> 00:15:13,049
Not at all. It's your wishful thinking.

189
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:18,150
Fine.

190
00:15:18,150 --> 00:15:21,109
Have you read the messages in the high school group chat?

191
00:15:21,109 --> 00:15:24,109
Those from Year One and Year Two are throwing an alumni gathering.

192
00:15:24,109 --> 00:15:26,860
It's this weekend. Will you guys go there?

193
00:15:27,770 --> 00:15:30,609
My project is wrapping up.

194
00:15:30,610 --> 00:15:32,190
I'll be a bit busy.

195
00:15:32,190 --> 00:15:34,150
Zaizai could be working overtime.

196
00:15:34,150 --> 00:15:35,970
We'll pass this time.

197
00:15:36,490 --> 00:15:40,210
I can't be there. I'm grabbing a drink with my friends.

198
00:15:41,170 --> 00:15:45,190
But Zaizai said Jiang Jia would be there.

199
00:15:47,570 --> 00:15:49,309
Hello? I won't be there this weekend.

200
00:15:49,309 --> 00:15:51,889
Yes. I quit drinking.

201
00:15:53,670 --> 00:15:55,290
Are you free?

202
00:15:55,290 --> 00:15:57,010
Pick an outfit for me.

203
00:16:03,490 --> 00:16:05,949
Am I seeing this right?

204
00:16:05,949 --> 00:16:07,469
It's Gu Ran.

205
00:16:07,469 --> 00:16:09,749
I ran into him in the hospital not long ago.

206
00:16:09,749 --> 00:16:11,750
He still looks the same as he was back in high school.

207
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:13,889
I wish I could talk to him.

208
00:16:13,890 --> 00:16:16,369
But he's been frowning at his phone.

209
00:16:16,370 --> 00:16:19,090
Maybe it's something important.

210
00:16:23,350 --> 00:16:26,050
My right profile looks better.

211
00:16:30,410 --> 00:16:32,650
They will come in from the front door

212
00:16:32,650 --> 00:16:34,870
and see my perfect side profile.

213
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:37,370
They will be stunned by my charm.

214
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:18,670
What are you staring at?

215
00:17:21,710 --> 00:17:24,890
You look different tonight.

216
00:17:25,650 --> 00:17:26,869
Do I look good?

217
00:17:26,869 --> 00:17:29,169
I bought this dress this afternoon.

218
00:17:29,169 --> 00:17:32,470
But then again, I've never tried this appearance.

219
00:17:32,470 --> 00:17:34,169
Does it look strange?

220
00:17:34,170 --> 00:17:37,570
Not at all. You look great.

221
00:17:53,370 --> 00:17:55,209
Should we...

222
00:17:55,209 --> 00:17:56,920
Jiang Jia.

223
00:17:57,509 --> 00:18:01,709
May... I have this dance?

224
00:18:01,709 --> 00:18:04,270
I can't really dance.

225
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:06,269
Yes. She doesn't dance well.

226
00:18:06,269 --> 00:18:09,510
It's all right. I can show you the steps.

227
00:18:09,510 --> 00:18:12,090
I'm a slow learner.

228
00:18:12,090 --> 00:18:14,050
Slower than anyone you know.

229
00:18:15,170 --> 00:18:16,270
- Give it a try. 
 - She is...

230
00:18:16,270 --> 00:18:17,970
Okay.

231
00:18:32,970 --> 00:18:36,650
Bro, do you know Jiang Jia well?

232
00:18:37,670 --> 00:18:39,370
What is it?

233
00:18:40,171 --> 00:18:41,689
That's my friend, Sun Yuan.

234
00:18:41,690 --> 00:18:43,249
He works in the same TV station as Jiang Jia.

235
00:18:43,250 --> 00:18:44,509
He's had a crush on her for more than half a year.

236
00:18:44,509 --> 00:18:47,670
Recently, he decided to take the initiative.

237
00:18:47,670 --> 00:18:50,070
As his friend, I came to ask

238
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:53,010
if you know anything about Jiang Jia's hobbies.

239
00:18:53,010 --> 00:18:54,850
You must know.

240
00:18:56,230 --> 00:18:59,369
Come on. You know her so well.

241
00:18:59,369 --> 00:19:01,570
Do your old schoolmate a favor.

242
00:19:04,190 --> 00:19:06,310
I think...

243
00:19:07,010 --> 00:19:09,350
I may not know her very well.

244
00:19:09,970 --> 00:19:12,470
Gu Ran? Did Jiang Jia leave?

245
00:19:12,470 --> 00:19:13,769
Yes.

246
00:19:13,770 --> 00:19:14,570
Huh?

247
00:19:14,571 --> 00:19:16,809
Why didn't you leave with her?

248
00:19:16,810 --> 00:19:19,470
What kind of boyfriend are you?

249
00:19:19,470 --> 00:19:21,070
What?

250
00:19:21,670 --> 00:19:25,470
Aren't you two in love?

251
00:19:25,470 --> 00:19:27,190
No.

252
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:28,590
That can't be right.

253
00:19:28,590 --> 00:19:30,409
Jiang Jia has liked you for ages.

254
00:19:30,410 --> 00:19:31,869
Hasn't she confessed?

255
00:19:31,869 --> 00:19:35,589
Hold on. What do you mean by she likes me?

256
00:19:35,589 --> 00:19:37,809
When we were having fun at the summer market

257
00:19:37,809 --> 00:19:41,050
after the NCEE ended, she said...

258
00:19:41,050 --> 00:19:43,190
 I won't be in a relationship with my friend. 

259
00:19:43,190 --> 00:19:45,610
 Being friends is not easy as it is. 

260
00:19:45,610 --> 00:19:48,369
 What if something bad happens after we start dating? 

261
00:19:48,369 --> 00:19:50,189
 It will be awkward if we can't even be friends. 

262
00:19:50,189 --> 00:19:52,770
 Yes, that makes sense. 

263
00:19:53,450 --> 00:19:58,410
 But if it's Gu Ran, that'd be nice. 

264
00:19:58,410 --> 00:20:01,449
 Oh! You have a crush on Gu Ran! 

265
00:20:01,450 --> 00:20:05,169
 No, not at all. You heard it wrong. 

266
00:20:05,169 --> 00:20:08,369
That's why she went to you when she arrived today.

267
00:20:08,370 --> 00:20:10,170
I thought you two were seeing each other.

268
00:20:10,170 --> 00:20:12,150
How could I be wrong?

269
00:20:12,150 --> 00:20:13,690
Thanks!

270
00:20:43,170 --> 00:20:47,270
